<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/820">أَنَسُ بْنُ عِيَاضٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> أَخْبَرَهُ <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَرَّقَ بَيْنَ رَجُلٍ وَامْرَأَةٍ قَذَفَهَا وَأَحْلَفَهُمَا.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>